HACKATHON_AUDIT_DETAILED.md
PROJECT_JOURNEY.md

# Plot artifacts are gitignored everywhere. HF Space rejects binaries on push,
# so the README references PNGs via SHA-pinned GitHub raw URLs that resolve to
# the historical blob in commit a9e723b — see README.md hero/temporal/training
# image links. To refresh the plots: regenerate locally, commit them on a
# GitHub-only branch, then update the SHA-pin in README to the new commit.
plots/*.png
plots/*.zip
plots/**/*.png
plots/**/*.zip
docs/assets/plots/*.png

# Exception: B.2 co-evolution plots are committed (referenced by README + slide deck;
# small enough to live in git, regenerated by `python eval/plot_coevolution.py`).
!plots/chakravyuh_plots/coevolution_*.png
!plots/chakravyuh_plots/scammer_phase1_*.png

# LoRA / checkpoint zips at repo root — these belong on HF Hub, not git.
*.zip
!notebooks/**/*.zip
